## Code Standards

### Language

- **Code/Commits/Docs**: Always English

### Commits

Always commit progress after completing a task.

```
<type>(<scope>): <description>

feat(api): add fleet CRUD endpoints
fix(web): resolve component import
docs: update project documentation
```

### Prohibited

- Task-specific comments
- `console.log` in production
- Commented-out code
- Magic numbers

## API Endpoints

```
GET  /health                    # Health check
GET  /api/fleet                 # List all assets
GET  /api/fleet/summary         # Fleet statistics
GET  /api/fleet/:id             # Get single asset
POST /api/fleet                 # Create asset
POST /api/fleet/bulk            # Bulk import assets
PUT  /api/fleet/:id             # Update asset
DELETE /api/fleet/:id           # Delete asset

GET  /api/scenarios             # List scenarios
POST /api/scenarios             # Create scenario
GET  /api/scenarios/:id         # Get scenario
PUT  /api/scenarios/:id         # Update scenario
POST /api/scenarios/:id/approve # Approve scenario
DELETE /api/scenarios/:id       # Delete scenario

POST /api/solver/solve          # Run optimization
GET  /api/solver/health         # Solver health
```
